de: A banquet was planned for honored guests, everyone got an errand for this auspicious fest. Aak would cook and Waai Fu should greet, and Hung went to Jaye for some freshly caught fins. The time to feast finally arrived, yet the guests... had no place to dine.
nm: Lee's Detective Agency: A Holiday of Two Hours
jp: Li Shi Zhentan Shiwusuo: A Day in Lungmen - Liang Xiaoshi Jiaqi
